471
00:36:03,500 --> 00:36:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

472
00:36:03,900 --> 00:36:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] I taj odnos s njim, bez obzira na to što njega više nema.

473
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:10,599
[SPEAKER_02] Je, je, je, je.

474
00:36:10,599 --> 00:36:12,360
