507
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,119
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

508
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:26,360
[SPEAKER_02] Pa znaš šta?

509
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:29,179
[SPEAKER_02] Mogu ti praktično govoriti.

510
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:34,420
[SPEAKER_02] Naučio sam da, recimo,

511
